OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy
OL,6,Fshowers will clear eastwards during
OL,7,Fthe evening. Mostly dry overnight,
OL,8,Fwith clear spells for some in the
OL,9,Feast. However, a few light showers
OL,10,Fremain possible in the west and on
OL,11,Fhigher ground. Staying breezy but mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FA mostly dry day, with spells
OL,14,Fof sunshine. An increasing risk of
OL,15,Fshowery outbreaks of rain developing
OL,16,Flate afternoon, turning heavy over the
OL,17,Fhills by the evening. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
